hopobject.body: I've just started at kamagra deals uk Shame that the court values contract rights over biological rights. If a couple own a house jointly and one sells it without the other knowing or signing, the good faith purchasers DO NOT get good title to the house, they lose. Yet with a child, the mom can sign it over for adoption and when dad finds out and fights for the child back, he loses and the contract is upheld. Travesty.
